   "source": [
    "# 🚀 N8N Workflow Editor for Google Colab\n",
    "\n",
    "Build a complete workflow editor UI from scratch using Python!\n",
    "\n",
    "**What you'll learn:**\n",
    "- Creating DAG (Directed Acyclic Graph) workflows\n",
    "- Building node-based editors\n",
    "- Visualizing workflows\n",
    "- Executing workflows with logging\n",
    "- Exporting/importing workflows\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Cell 1: 🔧 Install Dependencies"
